%e A341583 B to C is where disks s=1 and s+1=2 exchange which is geometric length 2^s = 2.
%o A341583 (PARI) my(p=Mod('x,'x^4-'x^3-'x^2-2), f=7*'x^3+5*'x^2+3*'x+6); a(n) = (7<<n - polcoeff(lift(f*p^n),3))/2;
